                      directory



ACCESS, ACC

ACCESS  (ACC)  Cancels delete/overwrite protection set with PROTECT.

Syntax: ACC <ambiguous filename>



PROTECT, PROT

PROTECT (PROT) Protects file(s) from being deleted or overwritten by
