target.

Syntax: COPY <ambiguous source filename> (<destination>)
        UP   <ambiguous source filename> (<destination>)


<destination> can be:

<directory>\<filename>
<directory>            ; destination file(s) will be named as originals
omitted                ; file(s) will be copied to the current directory


